In this section, "regulated counselor or therapist" means:
A licensed clinical alcohol and drug counselor;
A licensed clinical marriage and family therapist;
A licensed clinical professional art therapist;
A licensed clinical professional counselor;
A licensed graduate alcohol and drug counselor;
A licensed graduate marriage and family therapist;
A licensed graduate professional art therapist;
A licensed graduate professional counselor;
A certified professional counselor-alcohol and drug counselor;
A certified associate counselor-alcohol and drug counselor;
A certified supervised counselor-alcohol and drug counselor;
A certified professional counselor-marriage and family therapist; and
A certified professional counselor.
